{"id": "ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 757, "displayName": {"text": "Hama Sushi", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "A menu limited to sushi & sashimi, prepared simply, draws fans to this cozy Japanese spot.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213MVFYRnJPSFUwU2tSM2RWWkxVVVZ3UVhGVWFGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing dining experience! I arrived 10 minutes before they opened and was lucky enough to get a seat in the first seating. The setup is intimate, centered around two chefs who prepare each piece of sushi right in front of you. It’s served directly onto your plate, which ensures maximum freshness. I was able to try so many different kinds of fish, and every single bite was incredible. Definitely a must-visit, and I’ll be back for sure!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing dining experience! I arrived 10 minutes before they opened and was lucky enough to get a seat in the first seating. The setup is intimate, centered around two chefs who prepare each piece of sushi right in front of you. It’s served directly onto your plate, which ensures maximum freshness. I was able to try so many different kinds of fish, and every single bite was incredible. Definitely a must-visit, and I’ll be back for sure!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Amber Zhang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101505073030466646704/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ1-_lOS2dcKgALaca407VHxwlhj_-iDkwbneTeOGH-CFdShYU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-08T00:40:48.127166697Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213MVFYRnJPSFUwU2tSM2RWWkxVVVZ3UVhGVWFGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213MVFYRnJPSFUwU2tSM2RWWkxVVVZ3UVhGVWFGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wTUxVaGtaRFpJYTNaelRIcGtkWFJCTUhKc1VGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We had a fantastic dining experience! It's a very small place, mostly sushi bar seating and maybe two tables in a corner. The setup feels intimate, centered around three chefs who prepare each piece of sushi right in front of you. They serve directly onto your plate, some waitress refill your water, bring your drinks, but the chefs are the one passing on your food. The three chefs were very friendly and told us when not to use soy sauce with a specific piece of fish. The tuna, tuna toro, scallop and albacore toro was super fresh and amazingly delicious.\n\nI forgot to take good photos of our food as I was more focused on eating!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We had a fantastic dining experience! It's a very small place, mostly sushi bar seating and maybe two tables in a corner. The setup feels intimate, centered around three chefs who prepare each piece of sushi right in front of you. They serve directly onto your plate, some waitress refill your water, bring your drinks, but the chefs are the one passing on your food. The three chefs were very friendly and told us when not to use soy sauce with a specific piece of fish. The tuna, tuna toro, scallop and albacore toro was super fresh and amazingly delicious.\n\nI forgot to take good photos of our food as I was more focused on eating!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Isabelle Magnin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109697886464848215046/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVcTCrfdgXoAuw944HmpjW0FxwK8nX7vlwR_SvEntCrQxOjOI4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-04T20:22:15.254142018Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wTUxVaGtaRFpJYTNaelRIcGtkWFJCTUhKc1VGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wTUxVaGtaRFpJYTNaelRIcGtkWFJCTUhKc1VGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkalZEVXpWekZIYkhaVVoyWjBZMU5rYmpaVVVuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Haven't been here in years. This was my go to for sushi when I used to live in Little Tokyo. Quality is slightly worst now than before but still decent. I went 2 times this week and the quality of the tuna is different both times. Please refer to my photo to see the difference. Sushi gen might be the better sushi spot now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Haven't been here in years. This was my go to for sushi when I used to live in Little Tokyo. Quality is slightly worst now than before but still decent. I went 2 times this week and the quality of the tuna is different both times. Please refer to my photo to see the difference. Sushi gen might be the better sushi spot now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "EDMurse", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113159857898738270915/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjcPTrjcb-H73PiWa_KL28Xl6W7mGNiDW22cjTXuxPA-CeRg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-23T10:44:21.429213480Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkalZEVXpWekZIYkhaVVoyWjBZMU5rYmpaVVVuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkalZEVXpWekZIYkhaVVoyWjBZMU5rYmpaVVVuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSa01WTkhkakJhWm0xemFXVmlUbWh0TkVGNVgzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I have been here many times. Love their food. One of the best sashimi and sushi I have ever had. I preferred the old waitresses they use to have. The newer younger ones are okay but could be better. I would definitely go back because I like the quality of the sashimi and sushi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I have been here many times. Love their food. One of the best sashimi and sushi I have ever had. I preferred the old waitresses they use to have. The newer younger ones are okay but could be better. I would definitely go back because I like the quality of the sashimi and sushi.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "GeoMar Traveler", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103385321025956266063/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuAf52NMmc9q5NYSDFhIf8CLFIs8M3ZMwHloRL55xh_TLgJgd6=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-05-29T19:03:03.292544957Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSa01WTkhkakJhWm0xemFXVmlUbWh0TkVGNVgzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pSa01WTkhkakJhWm0xemFXVmlUbWh0TkVGNVgzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKa1JIRTFObVZyU0doS1RuY3djSE40VDJsTGFWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They have a strict no phones rule so I got this as subtly as possible. The sushi selection was limited but deliciously worth it. Service was outstanding too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They have a strict no phones rule so I got this as subtly as possible. The sushi selection was limited but deliciously worth it. Service was outstanding too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Randi L Rubin", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111459367325224700604/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf9_w_-227jviJo8GlH13Xe-0YSXuw25Sb4UE0VSwqUVYnwX_e=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-15T23:03:37.587838480Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKa1JIRTFObVZyU0doS1RuY3djSE40VDJsTGFWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKa1JIRTFObVZyU0doS1RuY3djSE40VDJsTGFWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/photos/AWCwydhCI9Lt_WYgbMIloj76_d1yIbH5NyJ5xJKmr9y2nRh1kGDTGnYF1Ul3FOvupp-uNGEbpOllLo8KAVf8eJwQ8DovTfAKDj25RSBFJe8lLM_ZYoXQeq1aV9ka4ENQqFyjQ748R7ArKlSOMLn_V_57SPtiMBQZt1XKxJE3beu9LLfVmJKEqyDCOtuoeRRGOu-SKnieNXTMWKy_Ws0eao2qKZUF0UTpLw63B1XfJHdoPalcHu2o5EDlgcTxudFWv-BPXylKoHV8qD7SthuBQm1gs3xUfTJnXn_VQFtNMNq78Tz2qeJdqF2uYth-s3dzpuP0BXgzRaJBOj0Piscvc7mxoj5jaRnW7y3VcCVyBn0kRfoI75zNUksNs2cDT4RpFEPi2nTdrbwtrv-oCC7jQI_1crJP1yTIVA3ZgsAxQcSlzc1ILT8", "widthPx": 2435, "heightPx": 2435, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Pam G", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/116989238648417207350", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjWnH1C910rnodeYwY8UoNu_K-APrJQSBEOYegjkBpQVmprGLoug=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICZ3Jia0QE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgICZ3Jia0QE!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2c647f97c34df:0x35afb5fd9db2813c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ3zR8-UfGwoARPIGynf21rzU/photos/AWCwydidRcClhOdWitzqCQRBy4XLuN4rsd74dOTqBoKh3dWAdjfx9g5vyArD9D3ZZHGjcxI283F5m